item.title: ROS Tutorial
item.description: This article focuses on the basic example tutorial on how to use HornedSungem in ROS. This document is only available for the multi-model version. If HornedSungem hardware version is too low, please update the firmware of the corresponding version. 1 Environment The operating system selected for our documentation is Ubuntu 16.04 Configuring the ROS environment (Recommended kinetic) ROS Kinetic ONLY supports Wily (Ubuntu 15.10), Xenial (Ubuntu 16.04) and Jessie (Debian 8) for debian packages.
